The box has a little slot in the top and a plastic hopper at the bottom.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
NUMBER 1143
NAME Abandoned Mall, corridor
*DESCRIPTION_START
Two plastic benches are pushed together in the middle of the hallway.
Beside them sit a pile of sand with flecks of rust and tattered bits of
paper stuck in it. To the southeast, a battered door hangs open from its
frame by a single hinge. Opposite the door, a red brick arch becons as
it did to customers in its heyday.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
EXIT NW 1140
MONSTER_GROUP 60
