NUMBER 1144
NAME Abandoned Mall, store
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is filled with scraps and chunks of corroded metal laying
in rough rows to the back of the store. Similarly, against the walls
are occasional piles of rust. A counter with a few small round holes
drilled in it reigns over the few plastic survivors of the ages.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
EXIT O 1143
MONSTER_GROUP 60
;
; counter
ITEM 0 470 LOCKED VAL1=75
;
NUMBER 1145
NAME Abandoned Mall, store
*DESCRIPTION_START
A long, shiny black table runs the length of this room and it holds,
spaced very evenly and regularly, alternating plastic and earthenware
dishes. Some tall but shallow alcoves in the wall contain more little
dishes and the odd plastic bucket.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
MONSTER_GROUP 60
EXIT O 1143
;
NUMBER 1166
NAME Sublevel 2, corridor
*DESCRIPTION_START
This long corridor stretches far to the south while to the north is
