NUMBER 1151
NAME Sublevel 1, wiring trunk
*DESCRIPTION_START
Many wires, cables, lines, and switches cover all available space in this
small room, although most are now mangled or corroded beyond repair. A
dubious-looking steel ladder leads down through a hole in the floor to
the cable trunk beneath.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 36
ITEM 0 66 ADJ1=310  VAL1=37 VAL2=1149 CLOSED LOCKED
ITEM 1 1108 ADJ1=272 ADJ2=310 VAL2=1153
;
IFPREVERB go 1
   IFVAR RAC ! 8
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 < 30
         CLEARVERB
         ECHO PLAYER One of the rungs gives out as you step on it.
         ECHO OTHERS A rung of the ladder gives out as %n steps on it.
         AFFECT 1153
         ECHO OTHERS %n comes tumbling down from above.
         MOVE 1153
         DAMAGE CRUSH 15 A dull thud sounds as body and floor meet.
         POSITION LAY
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
;
;
