NAME Sublevel 2, climate control plant
*DESCRIPTION_START
A large machine looms over you from near the center of this room, its many
ducts and and fans looking like the trunk and branches of some sheet metal
tree. The room constantly hums with the sound of operating machinery.
Substantial amounts of heat are radiating from the machine and its associated
ductwork.
*DESCRIPTION_END
FIXED_LIGHT
MONSTER_GROUP 36
INDOOR_FLOOR
;
ITEM 0 853 ADJ1=163 ADJ2=192
; ITEM 0 is a huge metal machine
ITEM 1 72 ADJ1=396 VAL2=1157
; ITEM 1 is a low opening
ITEM 2 66 ADJ1=310  VAL1=35 VAL2=1155 CLOSED LOCKED
; ITEM 2 is a door leading out to 1155
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM BEHIND 0
Near the base of the wall behind the machine is a rectangular opening barely
tall enough for a highlander to crouch in. With a little twisting and alot
of pushing, a larger being might be able to squeeze through.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
ifpreverb go 1
   clearverb
   ifvar RAC ! 3
      position lay
      echo player You lay down in preparation to enter the opening.
      echo others %n lays down and prepares to enter the opening.
   endif
   affect 1157
   ifvar PLRSINROOM > 0
      affect 1156
      echo player You can't move ahead since someone else is blocking\
the conduit ahead of you.
   else
      affect 1156
      echo player You work your way through the opening.
      echo others %n moves into the low opening.
      move 1157
      affect 1157
      echo others %n works %h way in from the south.
      affect 1156
   endif
endif
;
NUMBER 1157
