IFPREVERB north -1
   CLEARVERB
   AFFECT 1158
   IFVAR PLRSINROOM > 0
     AFFECT 1157
     ECHO PLAYER Someone is blocking the conduit ahead of you.
   ELSE
     AFFECT 1157
     ECHO OTHERS %n works northward through the conduit.
     ECHO PLAYER You work your way northward through the conduit.
     MOVE 1158
     AFFECT 1158
     ECHO OTHERS %n works %h way through the conduit from the south.
     AFFECT 1157
   ENDIF
ENDIF
